Thank goodness for the backups I left at Sourceforge. :) Although I
wish  I had backed up more of my gladiator stuff.  No particular
comment about which stuff I want back.

I'll have to rebuild my code to create html maps from scenario files;
thankfully, most of that was copying code from another function.

I plan on putting out html maps of all the scenarios I've created.

If Tom Ricket won't mind, I would like to do the same for all the
scenarios built into the game.

Telivido, if you wouldn't mind I would like to do up html maps of all
your scenarios up.

If anybody else wants to host a backup of these maps, let me know.

* * *

I still would like some feedback on how my Contest Entry looks.  Does
the horse look like a horse?
